    <text>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_470ea0d3">
            <lb />The Rolling Sweep of a Storm Tossed Sea
            <lb />–
            <seg ana="#phantom_body" resp="#np" type="topic slogan">
                when Phantom Fingers play
            </seg>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_25ac3298">
            <lb />These are the
            <seg ana="#phantom_body" resp="#np" type="topic">
                Phantom<lb />Hands
            </seg>
            <seg ana="#immortality" resp="#np" type="topic">
                of a thousand<lb />immortal pianists;
            </seg> their
            <lb />glorious genius preserv-
            <lb />ed forever, through
            <seg ana="#miracle" resp="#np" type="topic">
                the
                <lb />miracle of <name type="brand">Welte-
                <lb />Mignon*</name>
                reproduction
            </seg>.
        </div>

        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_a481e398">
            <lb />Thunder of breaking waves;
            <lb />howl of the hurricane; crash of
            <lb />thunder; or,
            <seg ana="#suit_every_mood" resp="#np" type="topic">
                with your changing
                <lb />mood,
            </seg> mesmeric lure of the
            <lb />Lorelie's song; swinging measure
            <lb />of the Blue Danube; love-wrapt
            <lb />night"when the moon swings low"
            <lb />... played by the master musicians
            <lb />of the century
            <seg ana="#home" resp="#np" type="topic">
                in your own home,
            </seg>
            <lb />
            <seg ana="#touch_of_a_button">
                whenever you wish.
            </seg>
            <lb />The <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon*</name> brings a won-
            <lb />drous gift to you.
            <seg ana="#exact_reproduction">
                With uncanny
                <lb />fidelity,
            </seg> this
            supreme reproducing
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_8599e7fe">
            <lb />instrument preserves the actual
            <lb />
            <seg ana="#immortality" resp="#np" type="topic">
                playing of immortal musicians.
            </seg>
            <lb />
            <seg ana="#phantom_body" resp="#np" type="topic">
                Their
                phantom fingers perform,
            </seg>
            <lb />again,
            <seg ana="#touch_of_a_button">at your command.</seg>
            <lb />The <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon*</name>
            <seg ana="#invisibility" resp="#np" type="topic">
                is
                invisible
            </seg>
            <lb />and does not interfere with man-
            <lb />ual playing. It is obtainable in
            <lb />practically every good make of
            <lb />piano, either grand or upright.
            <lb />Write for interesting brochure.
            <lb /><orgName>Auto-Pneumatic Action Co.</orgName>, <persName>W.
            <lb />C. Heaton</persName>, President,
            <address>
                12th Ave.
                <lb />at 51st St., New York
            </address>.
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_7a9b17c3">
            <lb /><name type="brand">Welte-Mignon
            <lb />(Licensee)</name>
            <lb />Hear it-in comparison. There's a nearby dealer
            <lb />*Licensed under the original <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon</name> patents.
        </div>
